    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >             </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >              <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145070/extras/0656201fbc08e0e7f099b99b6ce5cb7a.avif?t=1771170315\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145070/extras_big/0656201fbc08e0e7f099b99b6ce5cb7a.avif?t=1771170315 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ever wondered what a quadrillion points of damage per second looks like?</strong> <strong>Now you can find out!</strong> <strong>Start the adventure and feel this power!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>At the beginning you click People to stun them to get their gold.</strong> <strong>You spend the gold to buy new items and not only deal more damage.</strong> <strong>The more damage you deal, the more gold you gain.</strong> <strong>Your power will grow exponentially and you will become the best in the world!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145070/extras/29cb1b0c036eb0ca28a930ab8b012340.avif?t=1771170315\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>                                                             Buy 15 unique Items,</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> Which will help you deal damage without clicking!</strong> <strong>Learn more and more legendary items.</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145070/extras/2272747e061ea45c853035693d050df5.avif?t=1771170315\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The damage per second inflicted by the item will make your spend the collected gold to</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>get better and better and to become a legend ...</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145070/extras/670fb87f3a9b06aaa49f9e2993e0d994.avif?t=1771170315\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> Click and defeat powerful enemies.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-15 unique Enemies.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145070/extras/09c3d39abb3165013c8ba2be81c7b4de.avif?t=1771170315\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>                                                     <u>Attention to the bosses!</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Need to do laundry or walk the dog?</strong> <strong>No worries!</strong> <strong>Your heroes will farm characters and automatically collect gold in your absence, even when the game is closed.</strong> <strong>But don't forget to come back and spend all that sweet gold on upgrades!</strong></p>",
